name: Json
description:
Participating in various Nano projects since early 2018. Owner and maintainer of NanoDevList, [NanoLinks](https://nanolinks.info), [NanoTicker](https://nanoticker.info), [NanoHost](https://nanos.cc), [KeyTools](https://tools.nanos.cc), [NanoRPCProxy](https://api.nanos.cc), [UnrealNano](https://unreal.nanos.cc/), [NanoGift](https://nanogift.me), [NanoNodeGraphics](https://github.com/Joohansson/NanoNodeGraphics) and more.

Part of the [Nault Wallet](https://nault.cc) dev team and maintaining the [Tix Wallet](https://tixwallet.cc/). Community manager of Nano [Reddit](https://www.reddit.com/r/nanocurrency) and [Discord](https://chat.nano.org/).

Providing [education](http://nanojson.medium.com/), [videos](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwam3KyfHV1nnwtptoX2kfw/videos?view_as=subscriber) and participating in protocol beta testing.
